1. Download a release for the development platform
2. Unpack the contents.
3. Create a main html file (could be index.html)
4. Create a package.json file (app manifest with all the configs)
5. npm install nw-dev --save-dev
6. Tweak away the package.json!
7. bower install materialize
FORK HERE
8a. Install AngularJS, and create a directive to act as the title bar.
8b. Use nothing but jQuery (it is already added) to build the title bar. 

9. Generate a custom scrollbar with: http://mikethedj4.github.io/Webkit-Scrollbar-Generator/